# Dev profile — auto-loaded by `npm run dev` (Vite "development" mode).
#
# Seeds the SPA at the local dev kgsm-api (kgsm-api/scripts/dev.sh → :8090, auth
# DISABLED). Paired with the DEV-only seed auto-connect in src/main.jsx, `npm run
# dev` boots straight into the app as admin — no connect screen, no Discord wall.
#
# This is committed on purpose: it is the shared dev default. To point dev at a
# different backend, override it with an (untracked) .env.development.local.
VITE_API_BASE=http://127.0.0.1:8090
